headline: Quest Diagnostics Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: Quest Diagnostics (NYSE: DGX), a leader in diagnostic information services, today announced that its Board of Directors declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.80 per share, payable on October 20, 2025 to shareholders of record of Quest Diagnostics common stock on October 3, 2025.
